    public static interface Physicaloid.UploadCallBack
    Callbacks of program process
    normal process:
    onPreUpload() -> onUploading -> onPostUpload
    cancel:
    onPreUpload() -> onUploading -> onCancel -> onPostUpload
    error:
    onPreUpload |
    onUploading | -> onError
